\SE\SM[double]\SE[12]That was fun, right? Where should we go
tomorrow? \!\SM[double]\SE[12]I heard that if we go a little off
the beaten path, there are bears that appear. I've been thinking
about wanting to hunt them sometime.

\SE[7]Hmm...! Hunting might be impossible for a while. \SE[8]It
seems like the rumored new job is quite busy...

\SE[2]Maybe I also need to help out, that's what my mother said
this morning...

\SE[9]If that's the case... I guess there's no helping it...
\SM[nod]\SE[0]Yeah, I'll help with your work... Do your best.

\SE[7]U-um, this is completely unrelated but... Vita, um...
\SE[52]Is it true that you're someone who can like anyone...?

\SE[2]Yeah, that's right? I think it's because of my...\.physical
condition since birth, but...

\SE[2]Y-yeah... \!\SE[8]Because I'm a girl and you're a boy after
all.

\SE[3]Yeah. My mom said, You don't have to choose and It's okay
to choose someone you love the most.
\SE[4]Huh? Aisha, you know about that, right?

\SE[44]I've become stiff again... \!\SE[64]Can I rely on you for
the usual...?

\SE[42]Well, well... I guess there's no other choice...!
\!\SE[1]Then, let's do it in the shade. \.It would be troublesome
if someone saw us... \!\SE[42]No, it's because it's cool.
\SE[12]... You wouldn't 'do it' with anyone other than me, right?

\SE[3]\SM[nod]Yeah. \!\SE[2]Because, you know, I don't get that
excited unless I'm with Aisha.

\SE[42]Y-Yes, that's right... \!\SE[43]If that's the case, then
it's fine...
